acceptance_criteria[8]: TabBar component at src/app/Chrome/Tabs/TabBar.tsx renders open tabs from tabStore,"Each tab shows label, optional icon, and close button (if closable)",Active tab visually highlighted,Drag-and-drop reordering works via HTML5 drag events (no external library),"Overflow handling: horizontal scroll with left/right arrows when tabs exceed width","Tab context menu on right-click: Close, Close Others, Close All, Split Right, Split Down",Double-click on empty tab bar area opens a new tab (if supported),Tab dirty indicator (dot) for unsaved content